#: ../titles.rst:247
msgid "Importing Text"
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:249
msgid "You can generate text & titles in many different programs, such as Blender, Inkscape, Krita, Gimp, etc... Before you can import text into OpenShot, you must first export the text from these programs into a compatible image format that contains a **transparent background** and **alpha** channel."
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:253
msgid "The ``SVG`` format is a great choice for vector graphics (curves, shapes, text effects and paths), however it is **not** always 100% compatible with OpenShot. Thus, we recommend using ``PNG`` format, which is a great web-based image format that can include a transparent background and alpha channel. A transparent background and alpha channel are needed for OpenShot to allow the text to not cover up videos and images on the timeline below them."
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:258
msgid "For information on importing animated sequences into OpenShot, please see :ref:`animation_image_seq_ref`."
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:261
msgid "Installing Inkscape"
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:263
msgid "The :guilabel:`Advanced Editor` feature in the :guilabel:`Title Editor` dialog requires the latest version of Inkscape (https://inkscape.org/release/) be installed and the OpenShot **Preferences** updated with the correct path to the Inkscape executable. See the :ref:`preferences_general_ref` tab in Preferences."
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:270
msgid "Installing Blender"
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:272
msgid "The :guilabel:`Animated Title` feature in OpenShot requires the latest version of Blender (https://www.blender.org/download/) be installed and the OpenShot **Preferences** updated with the correct path to the Blender executable. See the :ref:`preferences_general_ref` tab in Preferences. NOTE: The minimum supported version of Blender is 5.0+. Older versions of Blender are not compatible with OpenShot Video Editor."
msgstr ""

#: ../titles.rst:278
msgid "For a detailed guide on how to install these dependencies, see `Blender & Inkscape Guide <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/wiki/Blender-and-Inkscape-Guide>`_."
msgstr ""
